# Bundle the runnable examples + their docs/data into the source distribution
# (sdist). The wheel still ships only the importable `ambertraceai` package, so a
# `pip install` user reads the examples on GitHub or `help(api.<resource>)`; the
# sdist carries them for source browsers / `pip download --no-binary :all:`.
graft examples
include README.md
include LICENSE
include py.typed
include ambertraceai/py.typed
global-exclude *.pyc
global-exclude *.pyo
prune examples/__pycache__
prune examples/data/__pycache__
prune **/__pycache__
prune **/.pytest_cache
